<p><strong><a name=prob><font color=#if3d55 ><b>PROBLEM 
STATEMENT</b></font></a></strong>
<blockquote> 
  <p>Make a machine that should climb up a 1.5 meter high cliff with the help 
    of a freely hanging rope (of given dimension) and burst the balloons kept 
    on the plateau above. The two competing machines would start simultaneously 
    from opposite side of the cliff (refer figure). The machine that bursts the 
    maximum number of balloons (lying in its compartment) in the given time wins.</p>
</blockquote>
