<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#1f3d55">Structure of the 
Competition</font></strong><font color="#1f3d55">:</font><blockquote>
<ol>
  <li> The tournament will be played on a knockout basis.<br><br></li>
  <li> There shall be a preliminary qualification round just before the 
competition 
    for all the competing teams. The time limit to qualify will be three 
minutes. 
  <br><br></li>
  <li> In the qualification round, each team will have to climb the wall 
in a 
    maximum time of three minutes. The time taken by the machine will 
