    seeding for the first round of the competition. The first and the last 
teams 
    will be paired, second and the second last and so on. <br><br></li>
  <li> The teams will be paired similarly in the next round and so on till 
the 
    finals.<br><br></li>
  <li> If any team is disqualified for any reason, the opponent team will 
get 
    a walkover to the next round.<br><br></li>
  <li> The teams have to be ready for the contest within two minutes of 
the announcement 
    for them to appear for their match, failing which, the judges can 
disqualify 
    that team.<br><br></li>
  <li> The teams must adhere to the spirit of healthy competition.<br><br></li>
  <li>Judges reserve the right to modify the rules if they deem it 
necessary in 
    order to preserve the spirit of healthy competition.<br><br></li>
</ol></blockquote>
<strong><font color="#1f3d55">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Finals:</font></strong><blockquote>
<ol>
  <li>The finals shall be a best of three.<br><br></li>
  <li> If a balloon is not burst by any machine during a particualar round of the final competition, 
only 0.5 
    points will be awarded to the winner. If the winning machine bursts a 
balloon 
    to win, 1 point will be awarded to the winner.<br><br></li>
  <li> If at the end of three rounds, the scores are tied, one more final 
round 
    will be played to decide the winner.<br>
<br></li>
</ol><br></blockquote>
